    <item>
      <title>乔尔杰蒂称意大利将难以实现 2024 年增长目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/italy-will-struggle-to-meet-2024-growth-target-giorgetti-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利财政部长吉安卡洛·乔尔盖蒂表示，由于会计准则修订，意大利今年的经济产出将无法实现政府设定的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/italy-will-struggle-to-meet-2024-growth-target-giorgetti-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 20:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
